snippet.title: Amber heard and elon musk split again
snippet.description:
Amber heard and elon musk split again 
The couple decided to reconcile recently but have already gone their separate ways, despite “caring deeply” for each other. A source told People magazine “Elon decided it was time to end it and Amber agreed. They both still care deeply for each other but the timing wasn’t right.” Meanwhile, Elon previously admitted his first split from Amber “hurt bad”. He said “I just broke up with my girlfriend. It hurt bad. Well, she broke up with me more than I broke up with her, I think … article continues ...
